item.title: Interactive Dashboard on U.S. Car Failure Data using RMd
item.description: Introduction: Welcome to the Car Failure Dataset Dashboard Project! Objective: Analyze and visualize data related to car failures to provide insights into common issues and trends. Dataset Source: Obtained from [source], includes information about car failures over a specific period. Dashboard Overview: Purpose: Interactive exploration of the car failure dataset through visualizations and filters. Key Features: Dynamic filtering by car make, model, failure type, and visualization of trends over time.
